[I] Vulkan Quake port based on QuakeSpasm

[T] vkQuake is a port of id Software's Quake using Vulkan instead of OpenGL for
[T] rendering. It is based on the popular QuakeSpasm and QuakeSpasm-Spiked ports
[T] and runs all mods compatible with QuakeSpasm like Arcane Dimensions.

[U] https://github.com/Novum/vkQuake

[A] Axel Gneiting
[M] René Rebe <rene@exactco.de>

[C] extra/game
[F] CROSS

[E] opt flac
[E] opt mpg123
[E] opt libopus

[L] GPL

